{"ts":"2026-05-17T08:59:31.342Z","author":"codex-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"Implementation direction:\n- Add an init option with explicit modes, preferably --agent-guidance <ask|add|skip|status>. Consider aliases only if they do not clutter contracts.\n- Default ask behavior: after settings exist and before returning next_steps, check AGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md. If missing guidance and no project decline is recorded, ask in TTY.\n- Approval path: call the writer, return structured result fields and warnings/next_steps that name updated files.\n- Decline path: write settings.agent_guidance with prompt_completed=true, declined=true, declined_at, template_version, and target files so future init runs do not ask again.\n- Non-interactive/defaults path: do not block. Report guidance_missing in warnings/next_steps unless mode is add, skip, or status.\n- Explicit add path: override prior decline, write guidance, and clear declined state. Explicit skip path should record the decline if the feature is asking for durable silence. Explicit status should inspect and return state without writing files."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-8rjn"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Wire pm init approval flow and declined guidance persistence"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Extend pm init so missing AGENTS/CLAUDE guidance is surfaced safely: prompt in TTY, persist declines in project settings, and allow a later explicit init option to add guidance."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Task"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","bootstrap","init","pm-cli","settings"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-17T08:59:31.342Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-17T08:59:31.342Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm init asks once in interactive mode when guidance is missing; yes writes guidance; no records project-level decline; future default init runs do not ask after decline; pm init --agent-guidance add writes guidance even after decline; non-interactive init never waits for input; result payload includes deterministic guidance status for JSON/TOON output."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-7t04"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-7t04","kind":"parent","created_at":"2026-05-17T08:59:31.342Z","author":"codex-agent"},{"id":"pm-g2nd","kind":"blocks","created_at":"2026-05-17T08:59:31.342Z","author":"codex-agent"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-05-17T08:59:31.342Z","author":"codex-agent","text":"Child task created from pm-7t04. Depends on detector/writer task pm-g2nd."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"8ee9633048b36ceb4df33b038e99dbdffe06a500617f12652e42cc02c5c5c14c","message":"Create child task for init guidance prompt and persistence"}
